   `printf '<<REPLAY>>'; cat "$ETUDE_INPUTS_DIR"/*` > "$ETUDE_OUTPUT_FILE"
   so every replay output carries the marker the original lacks.
   judge.sh (chmod +x), CONTENT-AWARE so the swap can't flip the verdict:
